# Cloud agent bootstrap

On every cloud agent run:

1. Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) and [CURRENT_FOCUS.md](../../CURRENT_FOCUS.md)
2. Ensure Godot: `bash .cursor/install-godot.sh` if `godot` is missing
3. Run `bash scripts/debug/run_tests.sh smoke` before and after gameplay changes
4. For visual/map bugs: check for `artifacts/dev_annotation_latest.json` in the issue or repo
5. End with the task report format in AGENTS.md

Full setup: [docs/AI_DEV_SETUP.md](../../docs/AI_DEV_SETUP.md)
